ROS-Topic Name: /&lt;namespace&gt;/mavros/payload_adc
ROS-Topic Type: mavros_msgs/PayloadADC

Response structure:
    std_msgs/Header header
      uint32 seq
      <span class="nb">time </span>stamp
      string frame_id
    float32[2] adc_voltage
    uint8 adc_updated

